tid":2235604,"uid":138197,"like":6,"dislike":50,"score":-44,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T22:43:36.000Z","msg":"我老母老豆成日食魚 完全唔覺邊忽醒 結論 樓主On9"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T01:28:23.000Z","msg":"乜撚嘢結論嚟？<br />\n<br />\nHypothesis係咩？<br />\n<br />\nExperimental design呢？<br />\n<br />\n點樣去interpret data？<br />\n<br />\n不過，咁又係，生你出嚟，仲養到你咁大，邊忽醒丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95f9d7e8afa4cd1d6c0fe78bf674dba83750150d","tid":2235604,"uid":286155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T01:30:47.000Z","msg":"食蔥先會蔥明<br />\n識唔識架"},{"pid":"100c470fce0fe891b169a9e77a3b9ce09cd9b414","tid":2235604,"uid":886,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T01:30:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/isXcFrS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FisXcFrS.jpg&h=151260a1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"668afcd09a2f6ffd0ade7c4c72ef3a1344bbf660","tid":2235604,"uid":161193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"986f451b2e2ecec74ae795917aae8576c265c3df","tid":2235604,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T22:26:51.000Z","msg":"食魚會使人變得更聰明，這句說話很大程度上可能是建基於不少魚類含有大量OMEGA3脂肪酸。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TWhPXKj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTWhPXKj.jpg&h=fe2fe1b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nDHA是OMEGA3脂肪酸的一種，有實驗證據(Ref1)顯示有助老鼠大腦發展，故此被推算能預防人類腦退化症的發生，又或者輾轉被認定可以使人變得更加聰明。<br />\n<br />\n無論如何，媒體廣告經常渲染DHA對人體非常有益，尤其是標榜魚肝油產品含有好多DHA，非常值得進食，這究竟可不可信呢?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(圖2)基於個別某幾種蛋白酶數量不足的關係，我們的腦部只能產生極為微量的DHA，而肝臟亦只能夠產生相對少量DHA，因此DHA的獲取來源主要均依靠飲食得來。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XXhHyg3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXXhHyg3.jpg&h=69ac7192&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但有研究發現(Ref1,2)，餵飼老鼠DHA的話，血液、心臟及肝臟DHA含量雖然的確有所提高，但腦部的DHA水平則無任何大變化。<br />\n<br />\n若然DHA無法進入腦部的話，亦沒能夠為大腦帶來正面影響。<br />\n<br />\n（圖3）經過一系列的研究後，科學家發現Mfsd2a是腦部負責從血管接收DHA的蛋白質(Ref3,4)，它傾向接收與磷脂LPC結合的DHA，而不太傾向接納其他狀態的DHA。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7PCPXJM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7PCPXJM.jpg&h=fe8b4de0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這亦解釋得到，為何單獨餵飼老鼠DHA並不會引起腦部的DHA水平提升，原因是它並不是處於與LPC連結的狀態。<br />\n<br />\n然而，這個機制僅是腦部獨有，因此心臟、肝臟以及脂肪組織均能輕易有效攝取DHA，以及與磷脂LPC結合的DHA。<br />\n<br />\n（圖4）有研究(Ref5,6)指出，DHA與磷脂LPC的sn-2位置結合的話，DHA進入腦部的效果會更好。但亦有研究(Ref1)指sn-1或者sn-2均無任何大影響。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NCrk4oQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNCrk4oQ.jpg&h=1f117ab4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這些在老鼠大腦進行的研究，能否百分百套用在人類身上還是未知之數。<br />\n但若然初心是想讓大腦攝取DHA的話，選購健康產品的時候還是留意一下究竟相應的DHA究竟是處於甚麼狀態為好。<br />\n<br />\n至於日常飲食的話，磷蝦油（Krill Oil)則對比魚油相對上含有較多與磷脂結合的DHA。<br />\n<br />\n吃魚會使人變得更聰明，日後可能要改寫成為磷蝦了。<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去<span class=\"blue\">Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單</span>俾一個<span class=\"green\">like</span>以及<span class=\"red\">Bookmark</span>，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=bW%2FimIc%2BBhL52Hx1BZusr3hUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=a85930e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「<span class=\"gold\">買一嚿/半嚿薯仔</span>」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=bW%2FimIc%2BBhL52Hx1BZusr3hUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=ec5d7198\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n有興趣接收科學資訊的話，歡迎follow IG: potatopigtongue。<br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://www.nature.com/articles/s41598-017-11766-0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nature.com%2Farticles%2Fs41598-017-11766-0&d=bW%2FimIc%2BBhL52Hx1BZusr3hUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=207609e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nature.com/articles/s41598-017-11766-0</a><br />\nRef2:<a href=\"https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0098299717301358#bib304\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fpii%2FS0098299717301358%23bib304&d=bW%2FimIc%2BBhL52Hx1BZusr3hUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=301b22b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0098299717301358#bib304</a><br />\nRef3:<a href=\"https://www.nature.com/articles/nature13241\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nature.com%2Farticles%2Fnature13241&d=bW%2FimIc%2BBhL52Hx1BZusr3hUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=635ea3c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nature.com/articles/nature13241</a><br />\nRef4:<a href=\"https://portlandpress.com/biochemj/article-abstract/345/1/61/34800/Characterization-of-plasma-unsaturated?redirectedFrom=fulltext\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fportlandpress.com%2Fbiochemj%2Farticle-abstract%2F345%2F1%2F61%2F34800%2FCharacterization-of-plasma-unsaturated%3FredirectedFrom%3Dfulltext&d=bW%2FimIc%2BBhL52Hx1BZusr3hUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=85a7109d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://portlandpress.com/biochemj/article-abstract/345/1/61/34800/Characterization-of-plasma-unsaturated?redirectedFrom=fulltext</a><br />\nRef5:<a href=\"https://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/abs/10.1111/j.1471-4159.1992.tb08353.x\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fonlinelibrary.wiley.com%2Fdoi%2Fabs%2F10.1111%2Fj.1471-4159.1992.tb08353.x&d=bW%2FimIc%2BBhL52Hx1BZusr3hUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=e08bbd59\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/abs/10.1111/j.1471-4159.1992.tb08353.x</a><br />\nRef6:<a href=\"https://journals.physiology.org/doi/abs/10.1152/ajpregu.1994.267.5.R1273?casa_token=1ZAjjbsr9IUAAAAA:GSyyUhEOi025bD-GJBWZFJqa8JrLt4HV9a9z3qqxJug7nP8x9bOoPUa1xJcixYkRJWXBWQ6ohZGHhw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjournals.physiology.org%2Fdoi%2Fabs%2F10.1152%2Fajpregu.1994.267.5.R1273%3Fcasa_token%3D1ZAjjbsr9IUAAAAA%3AGSyyUhEOi025bD-GJBWZFJqa8JrLt4HV9a9z3qqxJug7nP8x9bOoPUa1xJcixYkRJWXBWQ6ohZGHhw&d=bW%2FimIc%2BBhL52Hx1BZusr3hUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=716575b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://journals.physiology.org/doi/abs/10.1152/ajpregu.1994.267.5.R1273?casa_token=1ZAjjbsr9IUAAAAA:GSyyUhEOi025bD-GJBWZFJqa8JrLt4HV9a9z3qqxJug7nP8x9bOoPUa1xJcixYkRJWXBWQ6ohZGHhw</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T02:10:50.000Z","msg":"磷蝦油已經開始做成環境問題了。 <br />\n大量磷蝦被捉已經影響鯨魚的食物鏈<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7942135ae4abc8f53c9bc3e06b6f3ea6b293a7f","tid":2235604,"uid":54975,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"cae1e54844f143dada130d4d922c037e5d6002e9","tid":2235604,"uid":138197,"like":1,"dislike":27,"score":-26,"quote":{"pid":"d37dff13eba026971119253eaa958db4a524c832","tid":2235604,"uid":14423,"like":56,"dislike":1,"score":55,"quote":{"pid":"0bdb131105fc3361f6624d149123ea53ea8c0982","tid":2235604,"uid":138197,"like":6,"dislike":50,"score":-44,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T22:43:36.000Z","msg":"我老母老豆成日食魚 完全唔覺邊忽醒 結論 樓主On9"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T22:53:34.000Z","msg":"結果生到你咁蠢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T22:58:13.000Z","msg":"得啦得啦 講下笑 係到人身攻擊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T03:06:14.000Z","msg":"你話你老豆老